name: Servicio
query:
SELECT a.opening_date as "Fecha:DAte:100", 
a.name as "Incidencia:Link/Issue:100",
a.status as "Estado",
a.issue_type as "Tipo de Soporte::150",
a.customer as "Cliente:Link/Customer:300",  
a.subject as "Asunto::350", 
a.owner as "Creado por", 
a.iniciado_por as "Asignado a",
a.finalizado_por as "Finalizado por", 
a.description as "Descripcion::350", 
a.horas_estimadas as "Horas Estimadas:Float:150", 
a.horas_reales as "Horas Reales:Float:150", 
a.horas_reales-a.horas_estimadas as "Diferencia:Float:150", 
a.costo_1 as "Costo:Currency:100"
FROM `tabIssue` a 


where a.opening_date >= %(a.from_date)s and a.opening_date <= %(a.to_date)s
